channel.title: [Showoff] All My Models(meta)[Showoff]
channel.description:
These are all of my Creations in Metasequoia, I am going to start using Cinema 4D from now on so im going to show all of my previous inventions before I start over. If you want any releases just pm me and I will post the download link on this page. If you do download any of my models Credits [u]MUST[/u] go to me. All creations will be posted from oldest to newest.
